exthheader.author: Stephen King
exthheader.description: SUMMARY: International bestselling author Stephen King is in terrifying top form with his collection of short stories in almost a decade.In this spine-chilling compilation,King takes readers down a road less traveled(for good reason)in the blocbuster e-Book“Riding the Bullet,”bad table service turns bloody when you stop in for“Lunch at the Gotham Cafe,”and terror becomes deja vu all over again when you get“That Feeling,You Can Only Say What It Is in Frendh”——along with eleven more stories that will keep you awake until daybread.Enter a nightmarish mindscape of nurelenting horror and shocking revelations that could only come from the imagination of greatest storyteller of our time
exthheader.subject: Horror tales; American
